    "V. CONCLUSION AND FUTURE WORKIn this paper we have explored how empirical digital rhetoric enables an investigation of how RLHF-enhanced AI chatbots function from a procedural, rather than classical, rhetorical perspective.",
    "That is, rather than examining the persuasiveness of the contents of the messages generated by these chatbots, we have used procedural rhetoric to reveal the persuasive power inherent in the procedures associated with the messages' construction, as well as in how users engage with them."
